2-piperidone compounds such as 1-(t-butyl)-2-piperidone, 1-phenyl-2-piperidone, 1-(p-methylphenyl)-2-piperidone, 1-(p-methoxyphenyl)-2-piperidone, and 1-naphthyl-2-piperidone;
